column2: SELECT Distinct s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec     FROM dbo.SpecObjAll AS s     INNER JOIN dbo.PhotoObjAll AS p on s.bestObjID = p.objID     INNER JOIN dbo.SpecLineAll AS l on s.specObjID = l.specObjID     WHERE SQRT(SQUARE(s.ra - #) + SQUARE(s.dec - #)) < # and s.z > #     and p.r < # and l.ew > #
